original_title: Kenny Loggins - Live from Daryl's House
overview: American singer-songwriter and guitarist Kenny Loggins performs with Daryl Hall and his band to perform "Your Mama Don't Dance," "Footloose," "Im Alright," "It's Uncanny," "Danny's Song," "This Is It," "You Make My Dreams."
title: Kenny Loggins - Live from Daryl's House
